# File: .env.example
# Purpose: Template for required workspace environment variables.
# Fill in: copy to .env (gitignored) and set values for your machine.
# See: docs/workspace-structure.md → "Environment Parameterization"
#
# Only non-credential identifiers belong here. Credentials (tokens,
# passwords, API keys) live in the OS keychain — see docs/service-access.md.

# --- GitHub ---
# GitHub organization or user that owns the repos (identifier only, not a token).
# GITHUB_ORG=
